# Code Navigation — jCodeMunch

Use jcodemunch-mcp tools. Never read full files to find code.

```
list_repos                                            → verify repo is indexed
search_symbols: { "repo": "<name>", "query": "..." } → find any symbol
get_symbol:     { "repo": "<name>", "symbol_id": "..." } → get source
get_repo_outline:   { "repo": "<name>" }             → structure overview
get_context_bundle: { "repo": "<name>", "symbol_id": "..." } → symbol + imports
search_text:    { "repo": "<name>", "query": "..." } → full-text search
```

Fall back to file reads only when editing. Background daemon keeps all repos indexed.
